{"tid":89940,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"五年感情 話淡就淡","createTime":"2017-01-21T16:42:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T15:08:55.000Z","uid":62862,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b4e9694066f30d9a875c90486d62322b9db97ed4","tid":89940,"uid":62862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:42:33.000Z","msg":"女人永遠都係猜不透<br />\n你以為同佢好熟 成為佢生活既一部分 <br />\n事實上 你真係高估左自己<br />\n由散左個刻開始 每晚訓覺合埋眼就係咁滴 自問唔係一個易喊既人 <br />\n真係好無奈 想揾人傾 翻開電話薄 連一個信任既人都無 好想得到你安慰 但發下夢就好<br />\n其實仲有好多野想講 但個心真係好亂 好難受 <br />\n<br />\n無地方發洩 求各位巴打體諒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439b816b8f3b1b2e40d681c172af443f2500c364","tid":89940,"uid":22739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:45:18.000Z","msg":"女人係咁 段感情話斬就斬<br />\n之前一齊經歷過既甜酸苦辣可以好似無發生過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292d0d0f3b48b715f86f3ac07cac6dca58ea2b9b","tid":89940,"uid":65146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:46:21.000Z","msg":"有冇同居   有冇計劃緊結婚?"},{"pid":"6eae70722bb059ccb4e81340048b3afe448ee228","tid":89940,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:47:33.000Z","msg":"同感 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同男朋友分開左 , 每晚訓教個心特別難受<br />\n而佢 .. 頭也不回無半點留戀咁走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我既世界得番自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef34be9dd2d1dfbee532636477dae4b41fc2b86","tid":89940,"uid":44083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:48:22.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 早啲接受左佢"},{"pid":"5b131e6be9508f3a19ac13e860949e61ca139659","tid":89940,"uid":62862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:50:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇同居   有冇計劃緊結婚?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無同居 但日日見面 因為大家都住hall 所以每日翻學放學都一齊<br />\n真心有打算結婚 目標係3年後"},{"pid":"f221e6dd4469dd6d83cdf2fe4933601681bb5995","tid":89940,"uid":62862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:51:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同感 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同男朋友分開左 , 每晚訓教個心特別難受<br />\n而佢 .. 頭也不回無半點留戀咁走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我既世界得番自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n從來無聽過男仔講分手 全部都係月仔講<br />\n而我 從來都唔會講分手兩隻字<br />\n絲打分左幾耐"},{"pid":"9c635991cbdd9bfd7699d801ea3747a6f7b12fc3","tid":89940,"uid":62862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:52:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同感 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同男朋友分開左 , 每晚訓教個心特別難受<br />\n而佢 .. 頭也不回無半點留戀咁走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我既世界得番自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n從來無聽過男仔講分手 全部都係月仔講<br />\n而我 從來都唔會講分手兩隻字<br />\n絲打分左幾耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打錯字 女仔"},{"pid":"ed9f084d5c86dcf3bd90167f99c8f8ba4d137a0f","tid":89940,"uid":50790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:54:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女人係咁 段感情話斬就斬<br />\n之前一齊經歷過既甜酸苦辣可以好似無發生過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockq